  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7455e1b1af245b34c95fc9187c26d9ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: MonkIntroDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  npcName: Grieving Monk
  npcSprite: {fileID: 0}
  dialogue:
  - Traveller... please, a moment of your time.
  - A shadow descended upon my village in the night. It killed everyone. My brothers,
    my students... all gone.
  - I alone survived, but I am too old and too weak to face it myself.
  - The creature still lurks nearby, feeding on the souls of the fallen. It must
    be destroyed.
  - If you slay this shadow for me, I will give you my sacred charm. It was blessed
    by the monks of my order long ago.
  - It will make you far stronger than you are now. Strong enough to face even a
    king.
